title: Week 16 Preview: Playoff berths & titles on the line
itunes:title: Week 16 Preview: Playoff berths & titles on the line
description:
A room filled with heroes- Marc Sessler, Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal & Chris Wesseling- preview all of the Week 16 matchups, including the Vikings’ golden opportunity to pick up their 11th win (7:00); Marc and Dan face off in another VERY surprising lock-off (16:00); The Chiefs take on the Dolphins in what might end up being Andy Reid’s last chance to make a meaningful run (26:00); Can the Falcons pull off a comeback game against the Saints? (37:00); Gregg predicts an end to Jimmy G’s winning streak and locks up the Jags (53:00); and much more!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
